=Fateful Love=

20
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:38,980
=Episode 8=

21
00:02:56,540 --> 00:02:57,580
(Tianque)

22
00:03:30,280 --> 00:03:31,480
How is this possible?

23
00:03:31,760 --> 00:03:32,600
